TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRANSACTION_DIST_ID, AE_HEADER_ID, AE_LINE_NUM, ST.APPLICATION_ID, CCID, ACCOUNT_CLASS, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='D' THEN AMOUNT ELSE 0 END AS ENTERED_DR, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='C' THEN AMOUNT ELSE 0 END AS ENTERED_CR , CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='D' THEN ACCOUNTED_AMOUNT ELSE 0 END ACCOUNTED_DR, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='C' THEN ACCOUNTED_AMOUNT ELSE 0 END ACCOUNTED_CR, CURRENCY_CODE, DIST_BAL_TYPE, ORDER_NUMBER, ORDER_LINE_ID, TRX_LINE_ID, ATTRIBUTE9, ATTRIBUTE6, ATTRIBUTE7, ATTRIBUTE8, TRANSACTION_ID, ATTRIBUTE14, ATTRIBUTE12, ATTRIBUTE13, ATTRIBUTE1, ATTRIBUTE15, LEDGER_ID, 'RI' AS EXCEPTION_TYPE, AMOUNT, ACCOUNTED_AMOUNT, GL_DATE, GL_POSTED_DATE, DIST_TYPE, ELEMENT_TYPE FROM $$STGDB.ST_CG_XXCFIR_REVENUE_DIST_ALL_RTE ST WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM $$STGDB.WI_XLA_REVENUE_TRANSFER_INCR WI WHERE WI.TRANSACTION_DIST_ID=ST.TRANSACTION_DIST_ID AND WI.APPLICATION_ID=ST.APPLICATION_ID)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT SDA.TRANSACTION_DIST_ID, SDA.AE_HEADER_ID, SDA.AE_LINE_NUM, SDA.APPLICATION_ID, COALESCE(XAH.ACCOUNTING_DATE,DATE '3500-01-01') ACCOUNTING_DATE, COALESCE(XAH.GL_TRANSFER_DATE,DATE '3500-01-01') GL_TRANSFER_DATE, XAH.LEDGER_ID, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='C' THEN ACCOUNTED_AMOUNT ELSE 0 END AS ACCOUNTED_CR, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='D' THEN ACCOUNTED_AMOUNT ELSE 0 END AS ACCOUNTED_DR, SDA.ACCOUNT_CLASS AS ACCOUNTING_CLASS_CODE,/*ACCOUNTING_CLASS_CODE IS CHANGED TO ACCOUNT_CLASS BY VKOPPURA*/ SDA.Attribute14,/*Attribute11 changed to Attribute14 */ SDA.Attribute12, SDA.ATTRIBUTE13, SDA.ATTRIBUTE1 ,/* Attribute14 changed to Attribute1 */ SDA.ORDER_LINE_ID ,/*ATTRIBUTE2 IS CHANGED TO ORDER_LINE_ID BY VKOPPURA*/ SDA.TRX_LINE_ID ,/*ATTRIBUTE4 IS CHANGED TO TRX_LINE_ID BY VKOPPURA*/ SDA.ATTRIBUTE9 ,/*ATTRIBUTE5 IS CHANGED TO ATTRIBUTE9 BY VKOPPURA*/ 'RTE_ADJ' AS ATTRIBUTE7,/*ATTRIBUTE7 IS HARDCODED TO RTE_ADJ BY VKOPPURA */ 0 AS ATTRIBUTE8,/* ATTRIBUTE8 IS HARDCODED TO 0 BY VKOPPURA */ COALESCE(SDA.TRANSACTION_ID,0) TRANSACTION_ID,/*ATTRIBUTE9 IS CHANGED TO TRANSACTION_ID BY VKOPPURA*/ SDA.CCID AS CODE_COMBINATION_ID, /*CODE_COMBINATION_ID IS CHANGED TO CCID BY VKOPPURA*/ SDA.CURRENCY_CODE, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='C' THEN AMOUNT ELSE 0 END AS ENTERED_CR, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='D' THEN AMOUNT ELSE 0 END AS ENTERED_DR, COALESCE(XXCFI.ACCOUNTING_RULE_DURATION,0) ACCOUNTING_RULE_DURATION, COALESCE(XXCFI.ACCOUNTING_RULE_NAME,'UNKNOWN') ACCOUNTING_RULE_NAME, COALESCE(XXCFI.ATTRIBUTE10,0) AS CONTRACT_NUMBER, XXCFI.ELEMENT_TYPE, COALESCE(XXCFI.RULE_END_DATE,DATE '3500-01-01') RULE_END_DATE, COALESCE(XXCFI.RULE_START_DATE,DATE '3500-01-01') RULE_START_DATE, /*COALESCE(XXCFI.ATTRIBUTE14,'CG') AS SS_CODE, */ 'CG' AS SS_CODE, /*knarlapu:Changing SS_CODE to CG*/ SDA.ATTRIBUTE15,/*added by SABANIL as a part of RTEQ1FY15 */ /*Q1FY17 RTE XAAS*/ SDA.ORDER_NUMBER, /*ATTRIBUTE1 changed to order_number */ XXCFI.ATTRIBUTE21, XXCFI.ATTRIBUTE22 /*END Q1FY17 RTE XAAS*/ FROM $$STGDB.ST_CG_XXCFIR_REVENUE_DIST_ALL_RTE SDA
INNER JOIN $$ETLVWDB.EL_XLA_AE_HEADERS_AR_RT XAH ON (XAH.AE_HEADER_ID = SDA.AE_HEADER_ID AND XAH.BALANCE_TYPE_CODE = 'A') INNER JOIN $$ETLVWDB.EL_XXCFIR_REV_EXTRACT_ALL_RT XXCFI ON (SDA.TRANSACTION_ID=XXCFI.TRANSACTION_ID)
UNION ALL
SELECT SDA.TRANSACTION_DIST_ID, SDA.AE_HEADER_ID, SDA.AE_LINE_NUM, SDA.APPLICATION_ID, COALESCE(XAH.ACCOUNTING_DATE,DATE '3500-01-01') ACCOUNTING_DATE, COALESCE(XAH.GL_TRANSFER_DATE,DATE '3500-01-01') GL_TRANSFER_DATE, XAH.LEDGER_ID, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='C' THEN ACCOUNTED_AMOUNT ELSE 0 END AS ACCOUNTED_CR, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='D' THEN ACCOUNTED_AMOUNT ELSE 0 END AS ACCOUNTED_DR, SDA.ACCOUNTING_CLASS_CODE ,/*ACCOUNTING_CLASS_CODE IS CHANGED TO ACCOUNT_CLASS BY VKOPPURA*/ SDA.Attribute14,/*Attribute11 changed to Attribute14 */ SDA.Attribute12, SDA.ATTRIBUTE13, SDA.ATTRIBUTE1 ,/* Attribute14 changed to Attribute1 */ SDA.ORDER_LINE_ID,/*ATTRIBUTE2 IS CHANGED TO ORDER_LINE_ID BY VKOPPURA*/ SDA.TRX_LINE_ID,/*ATTRIBUTE4 IS CHANGED TO TRX_LINE_ID BY VKOPPURA*/ SDA.ATTRIBUTE9,/*ATTRIBUTE5 IS CHANGED TO ATTRIBUTE9 BY VKOPPURA*/ 'RTE_ADJ' AS ATTRIBUTE7,/*ATTRIBUTE7 IS HARDCODED TO RTE_ADJ BY VKOPPURA */ 0 AS ATTRIBUTE8,/* ATTRIBUTE8 IS HARDCODED TO 0 BY VKOPPURA */ COALESCE(SDA.TRANSACTION_ID,0) TRANSACTION_ID,/*ATTRIBUTE9 IS CHANGED TO TRANSACTION_ID BY VKOPPURA*/ SDA.CODE_COMBINATION_ID, /*CODE_COMBINATION_ID IS CHANGED TO CCID BY VKOPPURA*/ SDA.CURRENCY_CODE, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='C' THEN AMOUNT ELSE 0 END AS ENTERED_CR, CASE WHEN DIST_BAL_TYPE='D' THEN AMOUNT ELSE 0 END AS ENTERED_DR, COALESCE(XXCFI.ACCOUNTING_RULE_DURATION,0) ACCOUNTING_RULE_DURATION, COALESCE(XXCFI.ACCOUNTING_RULE_NAME,'UNKNOWN') ACCOUNTING_RULE_NAME, COALESCE(XXCFI.ATTRIBUTE10,0) AS CONTRACT_NUMBER, XXCFI.ELEMENT_TYPE, COALESCE(XXCFI.RULE_END_DATE,DATE '3500-01-01') RULE_END_DATE, COALESCE(XXCFI.RULE_START_DATE,DATE '3500-01-01') RULE_START_DATE, /* COALESCE(XXCFI.ATTRIBUTE14,'CG') AS SS_CODE, */ 'CG' AS SS_CODE, /*knarlapu:Changing SS_CODE to CG*/ SDA.ATTRIBUTE15,/*added by SABANIL as a part of RTEQ1FY15 */ /*Q1FY17 RTE XAAS*/ SDA.order_number, /*ATTRIBUTE1 changed to order_number */ XXCFI.ATTRIBUTE21, XXCFI.ATTRIBUTE22 /*END Q1FY17 RTE XAAS*/ FROM $$EXCEPDB.EX_XXCFIR_REVENUE_DIST_V_AR_RT SDA INNER JOIN $$ETLVWDB.EL_FND_APPLICATION_AR EFAR ON (SDA.APPLICATION_ID=EFAR.APPLICATION_ID AND UPPER(EFAR.APPLICATION_NAME) ='REVENUE ATTRIBUTION' AND EFAR.LANG = 'US')
INNER JOIN $$ETLVWDB.EL_XLA_AE_HEADERS_AR_RT XAH ON (XAH.AE_HEADER_ID = SDA.AE_HEADER_ID AND XAH.BALANCE_TYPE_CODE = 'A') INNER JOIN $$ETLVWDB.EL_XXCFIR_REV_EXTRACT_ALL_RT XXCFI ON (SDA.TRANSACTION_ID=XXCFI.TRANSACTION_ID)
